Electrochemistry: Don't be a weirdo like that Roy at the pawnshop who doesn't like music. You don't need *sounds* when you have beats.
Composure: Keep still! It might perch on your shoulder.

Kim Kitsuragi: "No. I don't hear the Col Do Ma Ma Daqua -- and neither do you."
